orum/viewtopic.php?t=41829\">Cutechess-cli 0.5.1 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ilari_Pihlajisto\" title=\"Ilari Pihlajisto\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 06, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43157\">Ponder=on in cutechess-cli?</a> by <a href=\"/Jos%C3%A9_Carlos_Mart%C3%ADnez_Gal%C3%A1n\" title=\"José Carlos Martínez Galán\">José Carlos Martínez Galán</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43654\">Cutechess-cli questions</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schroder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44518\">My wish list for cutechess-cli</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schroder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 21, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=44521\">Cutechess engines.json</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Allbert\" title=\"Richard Allbert\">Richard Allbert</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 21, 2012 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=44598\">CuGen - cutechess batch files</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Allbert\" title=\"Richard Allbert\">Richard Allbert</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44789\">cutechess-cli: starting from FEN</a> by <a href=\"/Evert_Glebbeek\" title=\"Evert Glebbeek\">Evert Glebbeek</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">